Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.39,0:00:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新機動戰記-鋼彈W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.59,0:00:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.06,0:00:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.60,0:00:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.71,0:00:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱著你被淋濕的肩膀 想溫暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.92,0:00:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顫抖的指尖 徬徨地在找甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.72,0:00:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的視線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.00,0:01:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲傷變為力量的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.44,0:01:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.11,0:01:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.75,0:01:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.45,0:01:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.13,0:01:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你死在這裡\N而我就抓緊榮耀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.30,0:01:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是輸給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.63,0:01:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是輸給飛翼零式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.24,0:01:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還不明白嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.78,0:01:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會輸給區區這種系統…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.32,0:01:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三十三話\N[孤獨的戰場]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.52,0:02:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常悅耳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.85,0:02:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到你也有音樂天份啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.65,0:02:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我自小就喜歡音樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.16,0:02:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彈奏樂器能令我的心平靜下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.33,0:02:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，聽來好像是悲傷的樂曲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.33,0:02:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你別再責備自己比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.40,0:02:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在戰鬥裡也有迫不得已的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.17,0:02:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，那關乎人類的生死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.21,0:02:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是說迫不得已就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.34,0:02:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我堅強一點的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.68,0:02:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦就不會有那遭遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.15,0:03:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾茵小姐，收到OZ的情報吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.02,0:03:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.16,0:03:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然特列斯大人仍然下落不明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.69,0:03:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但OZ和成為叛軍的特列斯派的戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.50,0:03:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在全世界激烈起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.27,0:03:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，戰況對OZ有利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.67,0:03:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為普通駕駛員追不上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.17,0:03:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD的機動性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.11,0:03:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為我們能和MD對抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.48,0:03:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是自大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.45,0:03:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.65,0:03:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先要有鋼彈般性能的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.98,0:03:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，即使出戰消滅MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.12,0:03:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰爭也不會結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.12,0:03:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我們親身感受過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.26,0:03:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,區區一個駕駛員能做的事有限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.66,0:03:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下…山克王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.30,0:03:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能安慰那種士兵吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.77,0:03:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡的確是休息之地吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.81,0:03:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，被血沾污的我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.84,0:03:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許不可在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.58,0:03:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想希洛也有同感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.69,0:04:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把在宇宙大量生產的MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.29,0:04:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派落地球上\N紛爭地域的新星作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.46,0:04:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穩步得到成效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.23,0:04:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全世界的人類親眼目睹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.47,0:04:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD的威脅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.34,0:04:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的權力正在擴大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.71,0:04:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那意味著羅姆斐拉財團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.94,0:04:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,支配體制的確立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.75,0:04:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衝入大氣層準備完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.65,0:04:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艇長，今次看來沒阻礙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.22,0:04:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來值得慶幸啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.25,0:04:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是高熱源反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.56,0:04:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機動戰士急速接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.99,0:04:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出現了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.63,0:04:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是托爾吉斯!不會有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.27,0:04:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二號三號艇被毀!\N只剩下本艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.74,0:05:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出動MD!迎擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.81,0:05:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全軍覆沒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.98,0:05:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人類沒理由能戰勝MD…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.69,0:05:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡是[匹斯米利安]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.30,0:05:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作戰完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.63,0:05:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收容托爾吉斯後\N馬上離開這空域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.90,0:06:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是閃電伯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.94,0:06:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我只懂得做這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.27,0:06:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝你，霍華
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.28,0:06:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小意思，我們只是盡點心力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.55,0:06:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用客氣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.25,0:06:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，我就恭敬不如從命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.82,0:06:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能拜託你再調整托爾吉斯嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.42,0:06:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做甚麼?沒受損吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.62,0:06:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有，我總是覺得反應遲鈍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.72,0:06:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是因為你的反應速度太快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.19,0:06:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到你在這麼短時間內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.00,0:06:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就有超越托爾吉斯機動性的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.63,0:06:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收容了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.97,0:06:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起，莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.54,0:06:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要作為\N傑克斯‧馬吉斯活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.98,0:06:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那也是為了山克王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.25,0:06:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯‧馬吉斯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.99,0:06:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，他好像以山克王國大使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.76,0:06:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米利亞爾特‧匹斯克拉福特的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.59,0:06:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上來宇宙，然後潛伏起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.86,0:06:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王國嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.73,0:07:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真棘手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.83,0:07:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪爾麥優候爵?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.73,0:07:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那國家提倡的完全和平主義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.50,0:07:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在仍得到很多國家的支持
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.77,0:07:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更不妙的是在財團裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.21,0:07:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那主義也正開始擴散開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.51,0:07:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.01,0:07:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉有無敵的MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.15,0:07:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒必要有那種懦弱的思想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.79,0:07:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無敵?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.22,0:07:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它被傑克斯‧馬吉斯擊敗了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.26,0:07:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.46,0:07:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一個降下地點\N是盧森堡基地吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.60,0:07:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，準備已經完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.87,0:07:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我今次不會讓\N傑克斯為所欲為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.30,0:07:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但願如此啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.37,0:07:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也試試對付他的親人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.41,0:07:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王國嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.65,0:07:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許應該趁這機會消滅她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.22,0:08:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來你在這種地方嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.03,0:08:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.19,0:08:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以坐在旁邊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.06,0:08:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨便妳，這裡是妳的國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.37,0:08:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.31,0:08:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，你為何留在我的國家?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.35,0:08:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若是以前的你，我怎樣阻止你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.52,0:08:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也會馬上前去戰鬥吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.95,0:08:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你曾經回去宇宙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.52,0:08:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，你的故鄉沒好好待你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.79,0:08:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你很難過吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.93,0:08:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但希洛你也不能停止戰鬥呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.57,0:08:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為那雙藏有辛酸的瞳孔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.67,0:08:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和初次見到你時毫無分別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.37,0:08:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.84,0:08:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打擾你們，對不起\N莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.98,0:08:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,桃樂絲，有甚麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.42,0:09:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是羅姆斐拉財團的邀請信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.69,0:09:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於OZ的功勞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.26,0:09:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世界的紛爭即將解決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.20,0:09:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.93,0:09:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於戰爭結束後來臨的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.63,0:09:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們想學習山克王國的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.14,0:09:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全和平主義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.34,0:09:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,於是，我們寄出邀請信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.01,0:09:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望莉莉娜‧匹斯克拉福特公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.84,0:09:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出席在畢萊梅舉行的聚會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.15,0:09:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恕我冒昧，我自薦負責引路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.82,0:09:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能和莉莉娜殿下一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.69,0:09:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我實感榮幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.23,0:09:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來，請上車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.30,0:09:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻煩妳，桃樂絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.27,0:09:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下，我也一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.17,0:09:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，沒那必要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.54,0:09:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為莉莉娜殿下是客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.97,0:10:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉會負責送她去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.91,0:10:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.91,0:10:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾茵小姐，拜託妳看管這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.09,0:10:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，請你答應我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.26,0:10:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不會瞞著我離開這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.63,0:10:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下，要出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.14,0:10:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.48,0:10:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓她去沒問題嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.82,0:10:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對羅姆斐拉來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.15,0:10:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這國家的思想是危險的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.35,0:10:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萬一她有甚麼不測…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.42,0:10:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.67,0:11:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，你打算做甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.44,0:11:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大量MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.44,0:11:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即將降下盧森堡基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.48,0:11:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盧森堡有特列斯派的根據地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.18,0:11:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉想一次殲滅他們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.29,0:11:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然一次過派這麼多來地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.89,0:11:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盧森堡防衛多嚴密也支持不住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.53,0:11:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果贏了，如此一來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.13,0:11:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD就會從那裡擴展到全世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.16,0:11:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能!你多厲害也不能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.60,0:11:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,獨自擊落這麼多MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.63,0:11:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若你無論如何要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.84,0:11:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.90,0:11:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行，你留在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.24,0:11:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.27,0:11:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還不可以死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.81,0:11:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在找到特洛瓦之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.00,0:12:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾，甚麼回事?\N希洛呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.33,0:12:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛選擇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.44,0:12:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最有可能戰死的戰場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.00,0:12:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消滅一個基地來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.50,0:12:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,數量有點誇張啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.60,0:12:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盧森堡就是那麼重要的據點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.47,0:12:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但用來對付閃電伯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.18,0:12:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就要那麼多吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.44,0:12:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使對手怎樣攻來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.01,0:12:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也只會全力戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.45,0:12:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盧森堡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.15,0:12:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前從聯合搶回來的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.42,0:13:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到今次要為了保護它而戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.26,0:13:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真諷刺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.97,0:13:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯，你果然出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.67,0:13:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有穿梭機別管托爾吉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.71,0:13:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衝入大氣層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.34,0:13:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論如何都要攻陷盧森堡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.16,0:13:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.13,0:13:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜‧匹斯克拉福特公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.13,0:13:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今日承蒙各位邀請，多謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.13,0:13:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們能和妳見面才感光榮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.47,0:13:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,桃樂絲，辛苦妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.70,0:13:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能為各位效勞，我與有榮焉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.41,0:13:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，我失陪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.31,0:14:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下，加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.99,0:14:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.79,0:14:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在就是妳大顯身手的時候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.79,0:14:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要令我失望呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.66,0:14:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王國能和平治國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.77,0:14:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的確全靠各位的羅姆斐拉財團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.57,0:14:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另一方面，各位的OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.67,0:14:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在全世界發動戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.11,0:14:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同是羅姆斐拉的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.64,0:14:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何會產生不同形式\N的結果呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.11,0:14:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是因為怎樣使用力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.35,0:14:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是由那個人的心決定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.78,0:14:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果各位真的渴望和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.95,0:14:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望各位\N以我的山克王國為參考
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.13,0:14:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了那目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.13,0:14:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我準備好盡一切努力協助各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.14,0:14:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.34,0:15:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳看來還年輕卻有堅定的思想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.78,0:15:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但山克王國之內看來有茅盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.68,0:15:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在哪裡呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.88,0:15:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我解釋吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.82,0:15:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.52,0:15:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人向我們OZ的部隊展開攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.15,0:15:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給予我們重大的損失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.76,0:15:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他自稱是山克王國的大使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.63,0:15:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米利亞爾特‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.86,0:15:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然他接觸過衛星，但之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.50,0:15:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他以傑克斯‧馬吉斯的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.97,0:15:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乘坐托爾吉斯，和我們OZ敵對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.38,0:15:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反應始終遲鈍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.02,0:15:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和OZ敵對即是和羅姆斐拉敵對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.19,0:15:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以認為\N山克王國有野心吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.87,0:15:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個駕駛員現在也自稱是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.50,0:16:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米利亞爾特‧匹斯克拉福特嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.27,0:16:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.27,0:16:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，他就不是我哥哥米利亞爾特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.81,0:16:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,匹斯克拉福特家\N是最渴望和平的一族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.18,0:16:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身為其中一份子的哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.52,0:16:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能會駕駛機動戰士戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.65,0:16:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，他有何下場…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.85,0:16:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也和山克王國無關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.33,0:16:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，這看來是我們的誤會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.16,0:16:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們就適當地親手處置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.00,0:16:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叛徒傑克斯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.64,0:16:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,懷疑山克王國一事，我道歉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.17,0:16:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，容我告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.65,0:16:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王國，果然棘手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.89,0:16:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好出色啊，莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.29,0:16:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧我看中妳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.37,0:17:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰爭果然不是由木偶先生進行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.50,0:17:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要由人類進行才行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.77,0:17:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此，也要莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.57,0:17:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更加更加努力呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.71,0:17:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.58,0:17:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在就救妳一命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.79,0:17:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,王兄知道我會這樣做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.92,0:17:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,於是選擇了戰鬥呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.43,0:17:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以傑克斯‧馬吉斯的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.01,0:17:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,護衛的MD全軍覆沒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.18,0:17:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，目標的穿梭機降下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.91,0:17:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能攻陷盧森堡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.78,0:17:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到此為止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.19,0:18:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盧森堡，別被攻陷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.77,0:18:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是新型的MD嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.77,0:18:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.14,0:18:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈01?為何會在這裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.15,0:18:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在盧森堡，戰鬥好像開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.65,0:18:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想去吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.19,0:18:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我被他阻止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.62,0:18:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.49,0:18:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要代替希洛保護莉莉娜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.33,0:18:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望是我杞人憂天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.99,0:18:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萬一莉莉娜殿下有甚麼不測
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.63,0:18:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就沒臉見傑克斯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.80,0:18:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾茵隊長\N剛才有匿名通訊來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.70,0:18:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它說莉莉娜殿下的車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.81,0:18:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會被MD部隊襲擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.64,0:18:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.15,0:19:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.98,0:19:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出於一片苦心也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.25,0:19:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我擅自來接妳，對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.89,0:19:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊啊，帕根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.13,0:19:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳看來神色凝重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.46,0:19:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聚會上有甚麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.66,0:19:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.20,0:19:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.02,0:19:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,柏根振作點!帕根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.67,0:19:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾茵小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.40,0:20:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說著多漂亮的話也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.13,0:20:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我救不了任何人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.30,0:20:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對吧!我總是要別人拯救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.77,0:20:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不需要武力的和平有可能嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.28,0:20:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全和平是不能戰鬥的人
